  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>Service areas, where our Viking stove calls come from</h2>
    <div class="area-grid">
      <div><h4>Bel Air + Beverly Hills + Holmby Hills</h4><p><a href="/beverly-hills/">Beverly Hills</a> · Bel Air · Holmby Hills · Trousdale</p></div>
      <div><h4>Pacific Palisades + Brentwood</h4><p>Pacific Palisades · Brentwood · Rustic Canyon</p></div>
